## 🖨️ 1. Printer Initialization
Because your configuration runs a standalone compositor (Niri) instead of a heavy desktop environment, there is no automatic system settings popup for printer discovery.

* The Action: Turn on your Samsung printer, open Firefox, and navigate to the built-in local printing network panel.
* The Location: http://localhost:631/
* The Step: Click on Administration → Add Printer, log in with your primary system user details, and choose your discovered Samsung unit from the hardware list.

